143
00:12:49,770 --> 00:12:53,232
– <font color="Chocolate">PRESIDENT</font>: <i>Senator.</i>
– Mr. President.

144
00:12:53,315 --> 00:12:56,944
– Thank you for having me.
– Senator Kelly, this is Colonel William Stryker.

145
00:12:57,027 --> 00:13:00,739
– How do you do?
– <i>His department has been dealing with the mutant phenomenon...</i>

146
00:13:00,823 --> 00:13:03,284
